OL,3,CGary Lineker steps down from BBC and
OL,4,CMatch Of The Day after 25 years
OL,6,FGary Lineker is to leave the BBC and
OL,7,Fis stepping down as the front man of
OL,8,FMatch Of The Day, ITV News understands.
OL,10,FLineker, who turns 64 at the end of
OL,11,FNovember, is the highest-paid on-air
OL,12,Ftalent at the BBC and is under
OL,13,Fcontract until the end of the football
OL,14,Fseason.
OL,16,FThe news of his departure was
OL,17,Finitially reported in The Sun, with
OL,18,Fthe newspaper saying a BBC source told
OL,19,Fthem of his departure.
