OL,6,FThe Mirror reported the same news
OL,7,Fearlier this year, citing an internal
OL,8,FBBC email that was allegedly leaked
OL,9,Fand suggested an announcement over his
OL,10,Fexit was being drawn up.
OL,12,FThis was subsequently denied, with the
OL,13,Fcorporation suggesting discussions
OL,14,Fwere still ongoing over new terms.
OL,16,FLineker has previously laughed off the
OL,17,Fspeculation, joking that a Match of
OL,18,Fthe Day show in early October was his
OL,19,F"final" one, before adding: "before
OL,20,Fthe international break".
