OL,4,CMatch Of The Day after 25 years
OL,6,FThe 63-year-old also oversees a
OL,7,Fsuccessful podcast business, which
OL,8,Fincludes the popular The Rest Is
OL,9,FFootball, which he hosts alongside
OL,10,FMatch Of The Day pundits Alan Shearer
OL,11,Fand Micah Richards.
OL,13,FThe former England, Tottenham and
OL,14,FBarcelona striker took over the BBC's
OL,15,Fflagship football highlights show in
OL,16,F1999 after predecessor Des Lynam
OL,17,Fjoined ITV.
